Read proteingroups/phosphosites

read_proteingroups.Rd

Read proteingroups/phosphosites

read_proteingroups(
  proteinfile,
  quantity = guess_maxquant_quantity(proteinfile),
  designfile = default_designfile(proteinfile, "maxquant", quantity),
  select_subgroups = NULL,
  contaminants = FALSE,
  reverse = FALSE,
  fastafile = NULL,
  invert_subgroups = character(0),
  impute = stri_detect_regex(quantity, "[Ii]ntensity"),
  formula = if (single_subgroup(object)) ~1 else ~0 + subgroup,
  contrastdefs = contrast_subgroups(object),
  verbose = TRUE,
  plot = TRUE
)

read_phosphosites(
  phosphofile,
  proteinfile = paste0(dirname(phosphofile), "/proteinGroups.txt"),
  quantity = guess_maxquant_quantity(phosphofile),
  designfile = default_designfile(proteinfile, "maxquant", quantity),
  select_subgroups = NULL,
  contaminants = FALSE,
  reverse = FALSE,
  min_localization_prob = 0.75,
  fastafile = NULL,
  invert_subgroups = character(0),
  formula = if (single_subgroup(object)) ~1 else ~0 + subgroup,
  contrastdefs = contrast_subgroups(object),
  verbose = TRUE,
  plot = TRUE
)

Arguments

proteinfile

proteingroups file path
quantity

string: "Ratio normalized", "Ratio", "LFQ intensity", "Reporter intensity corrected", "Reporter intensity", "Intensity labeled", "Intensity"
designfile

designfile path
select_subgroups

subgroups to be selected (character vector)
contaminants

whether to return contaminants (TRUE/FALSE)
reverse

whether to return reverse peptides (TRUE/FALSE)
fastafile

NULL or fastafile (to deconvolute proteingroups)
invert_subgroups

subgroups to be inverted (character vector)
impute

whether to impute consistent nondetects (TRUE/FALSE)
formula

formula to create design matrix (using svars)
contrastdefs

contrast definition vector/matrix/list
verbose

TRUE/FALSE
plot

TRUE/FALSE
phosphofile

phosphosites file path
min_localization_prob

min site localization probability (number)

Value

SummarizedExperiment
